<p>Nile cruise dinner</p>
<p>Solar boat by the pyramids</p>
<p>Camel ride</p>
<p>Enter inside pyramid</p>
<p>Mummy rooms</p>
<p>Perfume factory,</p>
<p>Cartouche order &amp; papyrus Insitutes are for free (upon request)</p></div>

